          "en": "Use when a market's desire RISES with its own adoption — network effects, the strongest small-to-big engine. Below critical mass value is negative (anti-network: new users churn, the market collapses to zero — the cold-start problem); above the tipping point growth self-sustains. Seed a dense atomic network, not the whole market; the trendsetter cohort is that first cell."
